==English==

===Adjective===
'''coördinative'''

#synonym of '''[[coördinate]]'''

===Alternative spellings===
*co-ordinative
*coordinative

===Usage note===
*The use of coördinative in place of adjectival coördinate may prevent the ambiguity which may arise in the use of the latter.

